metadata.description:
Earth-78411, 66 million years ago: The asteroid threatening to extinguish the dinosaurs narrowly misses earth. Instead of apes, raptors developed higher forms of intelligence.

Being respectful instead of greedy by nature, today's Polite Raptors are now building a decentralized financial system, chasing the best upcoming NFT projects as a pack!
metadata.name: Polite Raptor #1
